KNYSNA - Mop-up operations are under way in Knysna.Officials say providing basic necessities is their priority.Blazes have been contained in the town, but firefighters are on standby for any flare-ups.The Knysna Municipality pleased to say the fires that have held Greater Knysna hostage for the past 6 days are all contained. #KnysnaFireKnysna Municipality extends its heartfelt thanks to the brave firefighters and logistics experts, #KnysnaFireHeros & volunteers #KnysnaFireThe death toll in the Western and Eastern Cape has risen to nine.Authorities will only be able assess final damages on Monday. UPDATE: #KnysnaFires controlled, contained - Mayor eNCA